51. A method for preparing the compound of formula 2.02

said method comprising
(a) reacting diethylacetamido malonate with guanidine hydrochloride in the presence of sodium methoxide and methanol to obtain a solid;
(b) dissolving the solid of (a) in an aqueous solution;
(c) subjecting the solution of (b) to an acidic precipitation to obtain a 5-formamino-2-amino-4,6-dihydroxypyrimidine precipitate;
(d) dissolving the 5-formamino-2-amino-4,6-dihydroxypyrimidine precipitate in an acid; and
(e) precipitating the solution of (d) to obtain the compound of formula 2.02.
